Package: fahb
Title: Design and Analysis of Pilot Trials Assessing Recruitment Feasibility
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Duncan", "Wilson", , "d.t.wilson@leeds.ac.uk", 
    role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7949-8718"))
Description: Find optimal decisions rules for guiding progression decisions 
    following a pilot trial, assuming a hierarchical recruitment model. Estimate 
    (probabilisticaly) the time until the main trial recruits to target, given 
    the recruitment data observed in the pilot.
